sql:
SELECT p.username, p.email 
FROM players p 
WHERE p.player_id IN (SELECT player_id FROM inventories);

SELECT item_id, item_win_rate
FROM item_statistics
WHERE item_win_rate = (SELECT MAX(item_win_rate) FROM item_statistics);

external_knowledge:
- "used at least five times" refers to the minimum number of times an item has been equipped;
- "most commonly used" implies items with a higher average usage rate;
- "win and usage rates" reflect the effectiveness and popularity of the items among players.

sql:
SELECT 
    (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM items) AS total_items,
    (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM players) AS total_players;

SELECT enhancement_type
FROM enhancements
WHERE cost > 100;

external_knowledge:
- "Gamers" refers to players in the game;
- "current gear pieces" refers to equipped items;
- "active arsenal" means the items that are currently equipped by the players;
- The "total power" is the sum of the 'raw' column values for all equipped items;
- "average power per piece" is calculated by dividing the total power by the number of equipped items.
